-
    helper=
        `I use 3 main prefixes: Local (+), Global (p!), and Universal (plx!)
        Local can be changed to anything you want, Global can only be turned on or off, and Universal cannot be touched as it is used as absolute fallback in case someone familiar with the me but unbeknownst your server setup can use my commands.   
        `
+section("Prefix","How to trigger my commands","prefix",".fas.fa-terminal",helper)
    .plx-flex(style="align-items:center").plx-grid
        .plx-flex-start.plx-width-1-1(class="plx-width-1-2@m")
