-
    helper=
        `
        You can enable and disable Local and Global Levelups independently.
        By enabling <b>Global</b> LevelUps you are also enabling DM Notifications to tell users when they receive Level prizes (Lootboxes), this action can be customized per-channel. If the user levels up where they can see the leveling message, they'll receive a DM, otherwise they won't.
        <b>Local LevelUps</b> in the other hand are more discrete, they only tell the new level and any roles they might've unlocked. You can <a href="#customlocallv">customize Local LevelUp messages here</a>.
        Local LevelUps <b>does not award Lootboxes</b>.
        `
+section("Level Ups","Notify people about their Level going up","levelupmsgs",".far.fa-arrow-alt-circle-up",helper)
