        .plx-flex-end.plx-width-1-1(class="plx-width-1-2@m")
            +pinkSwitch("levelup-global","Enable <b>Global</b> LevelUps",serverData.modules.LVUP )
        p.plx-margin-remove-bottom Custom Local Level Up message
        .plx-pink-input
            textarea#level-message(name="level-message", cols="25", rows="4")= serverData.modules.LVUP_text ||""






-
    helper=
        `
       Lootboxes are my most precious gifts to award server activity. They contain lots of items to boost your profile and unlock more items for you to play with.
       Each message from a conversation including a set amount of members has a 0.025% chance of spawning a box.

       Be wary that <b>forcing drops or farming boxes is not allowed and it is bannable</b>. You're risking to lose all your progress and items regardless of they being acquired legitimately before you were caught. 
